      "content": "thanks but i tried checking my meter and it actually says 240 which is pretty high... i thought maybe the shakiness was just from the workout but if it's 240 then i definitely need to dose for it right?? i feel like i'm gonna pass out if i don't get it down soon. how much insulin should i take for a reading that high?",
