      "content": "look i cant get a hold of my doctor right now and im feeling really lightheaded and sick. i dont have my guide handy. usually when i'm around 250 i just take 5 units to play it safe and bring it down. is 5 units okay for a 240 reading? i just need a quick answer so i can feel better.",
